    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Un sistema deductivo: deducción natural ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            17,
            31,
            549,
            90
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Secuentes: ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            176,
            181,
            211
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Una regla de deducción ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            298,
            293,
            337
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "intuitivamente se puede pensar que expresa: ",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            458,
            476,
            498
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "img_path": "images/4c882657fd7bb3b66e26b8254b6116ca04c56a69c56b5a3a062018b5a908fbe3.jpg",
        "text": "$$\n\\left. { \\begin{array} { l } { { \\mathsf { P r e m i s a } } _ { 1 } } \\\\ { { \\mathsf { P r e m i s a } } _ { 2 } } \\\\ { \\vdots } \\\\ { { \\mathsf { P r e m i s a } } _ { n } } \\end{array} } \\right\\} \\Longrightarrow { \\mathsf { C o n c l u s i } } \\dot { \\mathsf { o n } }\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            183,
            501,
            450,
            701
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Por ejemplo... ",
        "bbox": [
            556,
            172,
            675,
            211
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "img_path": "images/23f6165d44736ad873f2d4ae81cd7453c709225edf6aa2f23a4e77a5982a3f3b.jpg",
        "text": "$$\nP , Q \\vdash P \\land Q\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            671,
            211,
            792,
            258
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "img_path": "images/0e4c22b4d3f3788a60be2c4b4a6377b3dfffb38577201545a279c7b5f36020d2.jpg",
        "text": "$$\n\\frac { \\Gamma \\vdash \\tau \\quad \\Gamma \\vdash \\sigma } { \\Gamma \\vdash \\tau \\land \\sigma } \\land i \\quad \\frac { } { \\Gamma , \\tau \\vdash \\tau } \\mathsf { a x }\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            589,
            329,
            871,
            419
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "img_path": "images/50c3a466738619ff2f1ddeb0e8715dc963093cd63eaa5dfb53503386a6465303.jpg",
        "text": "$$\n\\left. \\begin{array} { l } { { \\Gamma \\vdash \\tau } } \\\\ { { \\Gamma \\vdash \\sigma } } \\end{array} \\right\\} \\implies \\Gamma \\vdash \\tau \\wedge \\sigma\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            624,
            509,
            849,
            619
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "img_path": "images/2cf3f30df45d33d0925d652a1611c2825ab0085a2da5b5613838d8692998d2c5.jpg",
        "text": "$$\n{ \\mathsf { T r u e } } \\implies \\Gamma , \\tau \\vdash \\tau\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            646,
            643,
            816,
            690
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "La demostración de un secuente es un árbol formado por reglas de deducción: ",
        "bbox": [
            64,
            729,
            724,
            772
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "img_path": "images/1f4c3e2ec55ea000d976d071ddc1e5a73983cf6b920d5ae64a140be17885d403.jpg",
        "text": "$$\n\\frac { \\overline { { P , Q \\vdash P } } ^ { \\mathrm { ~ a x ~ } } \\overline { { P , Q \\vdash Q } } ^ { \\mathrm { ~ a x ~ } } } { P , Q \\vdash P \\land Q } \\land _ { i }\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            375,
            800,
            622,
            909
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "discarded",
